'''兰德·保罗'''（{{lang-en|'''Rand Paul'''}}；{{bd|1963年|1月7日}}），全名'''-{zh-hk:蘭度·侯活;zh-tw:蘭德爾·霍華德;zh-cn:兰德尔·霍华德}-·「蘭德」·保羅'''（{{lang-en|Randal Howard "Rand" Paul}}），美國[[肯塔基州|肯塔基州]][[醫生|醫生]]與[[政治人物|政治人物]]；於2011年代表[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]當選[[美國參議員|美國參議員]]至今。此前，兰德·保罗是一名專業[[眼科|眼科]]醫生，父親[[羅恩·保羅|羅恩·保羅]]是前[[德克薩斯州|德州]][[美國眾議員|美國眾議員]]與醫生。

==早年生活==
兰德尔·霍华德·保罗1963年1月7日出生于[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]][[匹兹堡|匹兹堡]]，父亲[[罗恩·保罗|罗恩·保罗]]是一位政治家和医生。老保罗是[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]的一名[[美国众议院|国会众议员]]，曾三次竞选美国总统<ref>{{Cite news |last=Alessi |first=Ryan |date=2010-09-13 |title=Paul's top goal is to cut federal spending |work=Lexington Herald-Leader |url=http://www.kentucky.com/2010/04/20/1231313/pauls-small-government-message.html#more |access-date=2021-05-15 |archive-date=2013-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015114804/http://www.kentucky.com/2010/04/20/1231313/pauls-small-government-message.html#more |dead-url=no }}</ref>。保罗是五个孩子的最中间一个，他的四个兄弟姐妹分别是小罗纳德·罗尼·保罗，洛里·保罗·皮亚特，罗伯特·保罗和乔伊·保罗-勒布朗<ref>{{Cite web |last=Stonington |first=Joel |date=2010-10-04 |title=How Old Is Rand Paul? |url=http://www.politicsdaily.com/2010/10/04/how-old-is-rand-paul |access-date=2021-05-15 |website=Politics Daily |archive-date=2020-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806195915/https://www.huffpost.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

保罗在[[美国圣公会|圣公会]][[受洗|受洗]]<ref>{{Cite web |last=O'Bryan |first=Jason |date=2010-10-25 |title=What Is Rand Paul's Religion? |url=http://www.politicsdaily.com/2010/10/25/what-is-rand-pauls-religion |access-date=2021-05-15 |website=Politics Daily |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107181748/https://www.huffpost.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，青少年时期被确定为一名虔诚的基督徒<ref name="AW">{{cite news |last=Wolfson |first=Andrew |title=Rand Paul rides tide of anti-Washington sentiment |work=The Courier-Journal|location=Louisville, Kentucky |date=2010-10-18 |url=https://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/courier_journal/access/2166776301.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Oct+18%2C+2010&author=Andrew+Wolfson&pub=Courier+-+Journal&edition=&startpage=n%2Fa&desc=Rand+Paul+rides+tide+of+anti-Washington+sentiment |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629024018/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/courier_journal/access/2166776301.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Oct+18,+2010&author=Andrew+Wolfson&pub=Courier+-+Journal&edition=&startpage=n%2Fa&desc=Rand+Paul+rides+tide+of+anti-Washington+sentiment |dead-url=yes |archive-date=2011-06-29 |access-date=2021-05-15}}</ref>。

尽管他父亲的[[自由意志主义|自由意志主义]]观点和对个人权利的强烈支持<ref name="AW" /><ref>{{cite web |last=Healy |first=Gene |author-link=Gene Healy |title=Rand Paul, Anti-Incumbent Republican |website=Cato Institute |date=2010-05-18 |url=http://www.cato.org/pub_display.php?pub_id=11819 |access-date=2021-05-15 |quote=Given father Ron's libertarian convictions, people often assume that he is named after the self-styled 'radical for capitalism' who wrote ''Atlas Shrugged''. |archive-date=2011-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111109005230/http://www.cato.org/pub_display.php?pub_id=11819 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但小说家[[艾因·兰德|艾因·兰德]]并不是他名字的灵感来源。长大后，他改名为“兰迪”<ref name="NYT1">{{cite news |last=Leibovich |first=Mark |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2010/06/06/us/politics/06paul.html?_r=1&pagewanted=all |title=For Paul Family, Libertarian Ethos Began at Home |work=The New York Times |access-date=2021-05-15 |date=2010-06-06 |archive-date=2019-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190816164653/https://www.nytimes.com/2010/06/06/us/politics/06paul.html?_r=1&pagewanted=all |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但他的妻子把它缩短为“兰德”<ref name="AW"/><ref name="JR">{{cite web |last=Rettig |first=Jessica |url=http://politics.usnews.com/news/articles/2010/06/03/10-things-you-didnt-know-about-rand-paul.html |title=10 Things You Didn't Know About Rand Paul |work=U.S. News & World Report |access-date=2021-05-15 |date=2010-06-03 |archive-date=2010-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100906073351/http://politics.usnews.com/news/articles/2010/06/03/10-things-you-didnt-know-about-rand-paul.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine |last=Burnette |first=Eric |url=http://www.louisville.com/content/gospel-according-paul-louisville-magazines-inside-look-us-senate-candidate-rand-paul-news |title=The Gospel According to Paul |magazine=Louisville |access-date=2021-05-15 |date=2010-09-07 |archive-date=2013-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131013100622/http://www.louisville.com/content/gospel-according-paul-louisville-magazines-inside-look-us-senate-candidate-rand-paul-news |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

保罗一家于1968年搬到[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]的{{le|杰克逊湖 (得克萨斯州)|Lake Jackson, Texas|杰克逊湖}}<ref name="NYT1"/><ref name="WM"/>，保罗在这里长大<ref name="JH">{{cite news |last=Horowitz |first=Jason |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2010/02/03/AR2010020303643.html |title=Running for Senate, Rand Paul lights a fire under Kentucky GOP |work=The Washington Post |access-date=2021-05-25 |date=2010-02-04 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109032414/https://www.washingtonpost.com/gdpr-consent/?next_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fwp-dyn%2Fcontent%2Farticle%2F2010%2F02%2F03%2FAR2010020303643.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last= Wolfford |first= David |url= http://www.nationalreview.com/articles/229456/rand-against-machine/david-wolfford |title= Rand against the Machine |work= National Review |access-date= 2021-05-25 |date= 2010-04-05 |archive-date= 2013-11-01 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131101155643/http://www.nationalreview.com/articles/229456/rand-against-machine/david-wolfford |dead-url= no }}</ref>。他的父亲在此处开始行医，有一段时间他是[[布拉佐里亚县|布拉佐里亚县]]唯一的[[产科学|产科医生]]<ref name="NYT1"/><ref name="WM">{{Cite book |last=Watterson |first=Mark |title=Don't Weep for Me, America: How Democracy in America Became the Prince (While We Slept) |publisher=Dorrance Publishing |year=2008 |page=203 |isbn=978-0-8059-7890-2}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Sherman |first=Jerome L. |url=http://www.post-gazette.com/pg/07215/806597-176.stm |title=Texas congressman brings presidential campaign to hometown |work=Pittsburgh Post-Gazette |access-date=2021-05-25 |date=2007-08-03 |quote=He and his wife decided to settle in the southeastern Texan town of Lake Jackson, near the site of his military service. For a period, Paul was the only obstetrician in Brazoria County, and he delivered as many as 50 babies a month. |archive-date=2011-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110628180945/http://www.post-gazette.com/pg/07215/806597-176.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

兰德·保罗13岁时，他的父亲被选入[[美国众议院|美国众议院]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Straub |first=Bill |url=http://www.courierpress.com/news/2010/sep/19/rand-paul/ |title=Off and running: Rand Paul |work=Evansville Courier & Press |access-date=2021-05-25 |date=2010-09-19 |archive-date=2013-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130719173116/http://www.courierpress.com/news/2010/sep/19/rand-paul/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年，保罗参加了{{le|1976年共和党全国代表大会|1976 Republican National Convention}}，他的父亲是[[罗纳德·里根|罗纳德·里根]]的德克萨斯州代表团团长<ref name=RLizza>{{cite web |last1=Lizza |first1=Ryan |title=The Revenge of Rand Paul |url=https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2014/10/06/revenge-rand-paul |access-date=2021-05-25 |work=The New Yorker |date=2014-10-06 |archive-date=2021-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105064528/https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2014/10/06/revenge-rand-paul |dead-url=no }}</ref>。年轻的保罗经常在他父亲的国会办公室度过暑假实习<ref name= "Intellectual Inheritance">{{cite news |title=Rand Paul's Mixed Inheritance |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/01/26/us/politics/rand-pauls-mixed-inheritance.html |access-date=2021-05-25 |newspaper=The New York Times |date=2014-01-25 |author-link1=Sam Tanenhaus |first1=Sam |last1=Tanenhaus |author-link2=Jim Rutenberg |first2=Jim |last2=Rutenberg |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112040840/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/01/26/us/politics/rand-pauls-mixed-inheritance.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在他十几岁时，保罗研究了他父亲所尊敬的[[奥地利学派|奥地利学派经济学家]]，以及[[客观主义|客观主义]]哲学家[[艾茵·兰德|艾茵·兰德]]的著作<ref name="NYT1"/>。保罗在{{le|布拉佐斯伍德高中|Brazoswood High School}}就读期间进过游泳队，并在[[足球|足球]]队担当过后卫<ref name="AW"/><ref name= "JH"/>。

保罗于1981年秋季至1984年夏季就读于[[贝勒大学|贝勒大学]]，并参加了荣誉项目。在贝勒的那段时间里，他参加了游泳队和{{le|德克萨斯州年轻保守派|Young Conservatives of Texas}}，也曾是秘密组织{{le|诺兹兄弟会|The NoZe Brotherhood}}的成员，该组织以其不敬的幽默而闻名<ref>{{cite news |last=Brammer |first=Jack |url=http://www.kentucky.com/2010/08/11/1385157/paul-calls-allegations-in-gq-story.html |title=Paul: GQ allegations 'absolutely untrue' |work=Lexington Herald-Leader |access-date=2021-06-10 |date=2010-09-28 |archive-date=2013-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029200430/http://www.kentucky.com/2010/08/11/1385157/paul-calls-allegations-in-gq-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在校期间保罗经常为{{le|贝勒拉里亚特|The Baylor Lariat}}学生报撰稿<ref name=RLizza/>。保罗在没有接受[[学士|学士]]学位的情况下离开了贝勒大学<ref>{{cite news |title=Rand Paul's claim – twice in one day – that he has a biology degree |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/fact-checker/wp/2015/02/13/rand-pauls-claim-twice-in-one-day-that-he-has-a-biology-degree/?postshare=8041423829610892 |date=2015-02-13 |newspaper=The Washington Post |first=Glenn |last=Kessler |access-date=2021-06-10 |archive-date=2021-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105064604/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/fact-checker/wp/2015/02/13/rand-pauls-claim-twice-in-one-day-that-he-has-a-biology-degree/?postshare=8041423829610892 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，因为他被父亲的母校[[杜克大学医学院|杜克大学医学院]]录取，那时他不需要一个本科学位即可进入研究生院。保罗在1988年获得了[[医学博士|医学博士]]学位，并在1993年完成了住院医师实习<ref name="Degree">{{cite news |last=Brammer |first=Jack |date=2010-08-05 |title=Contrary to some media reports, Rand Paul has no bachelor's degree |url=https://www.kentucky.com/news/politics-government/election/article44043144.html |work=Lexington Herald-Leader |access-date=2021-06-10 |archive-date=2019-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190120111732/https://www.kentucky.com/news/politics-government/election/article44043144.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==医疗生涯==
在完成了眼科住院医师实习后，保罗搬到了肯塔基州的[[鲍灵格林_(肯塔基州)|鲍灵格林]]居住，从1993年起他在那里持有州政府颁发的医疗执照<ref name="lcj-2010">{{cite news |last=Gerth |first=Joseph |title=Rand Paul's ophthalmology certification not recognized by national clearinghouse |newspaper=The Courier-Journal |date=2010-06-14 |url=https://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/courier_journal/access/2059232451.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Jun+14%2C+2010&author=Joseph+Gerth&pub=Courier+-+Journal&edition=&startpage=n%2Fa&desc=Rand+Paul%27s+ophthalmology+certification+not+recognized+by+national+clearinghouse |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120725091635/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/courier_journal/access/2059232451.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Jun+14%2C+2010&author=Joseph+Gerth&pub=Courier+-+Journal&edition=&startpage=n%2Fa&desc=Rand+Paul%27s+ophthalmology+certification+not+recognized+by+national+clearinghouse |archive-date=2012-07-25 |access-date=2021-06-10 }}</ref>。保罗在唐宁麦克皮克视觉中心（{{lang|en|Downing McPeak Vision Centers}}）的约翰·唐宁那里得到了他的第一份工作。保罗在唐宁工作了大约五年后离开。之后，他在鲍灵格林的一家私人医疗集团格雷夫斯吉尔伯特诊所（{{lang|en|Graves Gilbert Clinic}}）工作了10年，然后在唐宁办公室对面一栋经过改造的平房里创建了自己的诊所<ref name="AVB"/>。保罗当选美国参议员后，将自己的诊所与唐宁的诊所合并了<ref>{{cite web |last=Harmon |first=Hayley |title=Rand Paul's Practice Merges with Downing-McPeak |website=WBKO |date=2011-01-05 |url=http://www.wbko.com/home/headlines/Rand_Pauls_Practice_Merges_with_Downing-McPeak_112968089.html |access-date=2021-06-10 |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110107095436/http://www.wbko.com/home/headlines/Rand_Pauls_Practice_Merges_with_Downing-McPeak_112968089.html |archive-date=2011-01-07 }}</ref>。保罗在1993年至2010年间曾面临两起医疗事故诉讼；他在一个案子中被判无罪，而另一个案子则被判5万美元<ref name="AVB">{{cite news |last=Van Benschoten |first=Amanda |title=Rand Paul's political rise surprises even those in Bowling Green |newspaper=The Courier-Journal |date=2010-07-05 |url=http://www.courier-journal.com/article/20100705/NEWS0106/7050340/Rand-Paul-s-political-rise-surprises-even-those-Bowling-Green |access-date=2021-06-10}}</ref>。保罗的医疗工作得到了唐宁的赞扬，他在鲍灵格林的两所医院享有医疗特权<ref name="lcj-2010"/><ref name="AVB"/>。2020年4月，保罗从[[COVID-19|COVID-19]]中康复后，开始在鲍灵格林的一家医院做志愿者，协助他们应对肯塔基州的[[COVID-19大流行|COVID-19大流行]]<ref>{{cite news |last1=Brammer |first1=Jack |title=Rand Paul says he has recovered from COVID-19 and is volunteering at a hospital |url=https://www.kentucky.com/news/politics-government/article241830831.html |access-date=2021-06-10 |work=Lexington Herald Leader |date=2020-04-07 |archive-date=2021-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105064551/https://www.kentucky.com/news/politics-government/article241830831.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

保罗擅长白内障和青光眼手术、LASIK手术和角膜移植<ref name="JR"/>。作为鲍灵格林正午[[国际狮子会|国际狮子会]]的成员，保罗于2009成立了南肯塔基狮子眼科诊所，为那些无力支付的人提供眼科手术和检查<ref name=mt>{{Cite web |url=http://www.kulr8.com/news/state/13944012.html |work=KULR-TV|date=2008-01-21 |access-date=2021-07-13 |agency=Associated Press |title=Son of long-shot presidential hopeful to visit Montana |location=Billings, Montana |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100525190721/http://www.kulr8.com/news/state/13944012.html |archive-date=2010-05-25}}</ref>。保罗因其建立南肯塔基狮子眼科诊所的工作而获得了狮子会国际基金会颁发的专门人道主义服务的梅尔文琼斯同伴奖<ref>{{cite news |last1=Thomason |first1=Andrew |title=Rand Paul's balancing act |url=http://www.bgdailynews.com/news/rand-paul-s-balancing-act/article_3134ce1f-d32b-5098-8127-2a8f8b9dd592.html |access-date=2021-07-13 |newspaper=Park City Daily News |date=2010-09-05 |archive-date=2021-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105064529/https://www.bgdailynews.com/news/rand-paul-s-balancing-act/article_3134ce1f-d32b-5098-8127-2a8f8b9dd592.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===国家眼科委员会===
1995年，保罗获得了{{le|美国眼科委员会|American Board of Ophthalmology}}（ABO）的执业证书<ref>{{cite web|url=https://abop.org/verify-a-physician/?fn=rand&ln=paul#physician-list-search-results|title=Verify a Physician|website=abop.org|accessdate=2021-07-13|archive-date=2021-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210531042215/https://abop.org/verify-a-physician/?fn=rand&ln=paul#physician-list-search-results|dead-url=no}}</ref>。三年前的1992年，ABO改变了以往颁发终身认证的认证方案，要求眼科医生每10年重新认证一次，而那些已经获得终身认证的医生则不需要重新认证。保罗觉得这是不公平的，于是发起了一场积极的运动，要求所有的眼科医生每十年重新认证一次。1997年，他成立了国家眼科委员会（NBO），以提供一种替代性的认证体系，其成本大大低于ABO的认证考试<ref name="WaPoNBO">{{cite news |first=David A. |last=Fahrenthold |title=How Rand Paul tried to lead an eye doctors' rebellion |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/how-rand-paul-tried-to-lead-an-eye-doctors-rebellion/2015/02/01/010994da-9cd6-11e4-a7ee-526210d665b4_story.html |work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] |date=2015-02-01 |access-date=2021-07-13 |archive-date=2021-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105064551/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/how-rand-paul-tried-to-lead-an-eye-doctors-rebellion/2015/02/01/010994da-9cd6-11e4-a7ee-526210d665b4_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Weigel |first=David |title=Rand Paul: I passed my ophthalmology certification, but took a stand against the way the board operates |newspaper=The Washington Post |date=2010-06-14 |url=http://voices.washingtonpost.com/right-now/2010/06/rand_paul_i_passed_my_opthamal.html |access-date=2021-07-13 |archive-date=2013-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130807014159/http://voices.washingtonpost.com/right-now/2010/06/rand_paul_i_passed_my_opthamal.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Montopoli |first=Brian |title=Rand Paul's Addresses Ophthalmology Certification Questions |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-503544_162-20007639-503544.html |work=CBS News |access-date=2021-07-13 |date=2010-06-14 |archive-date=2013-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131018074713/http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-503544_162-20007639-503544.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。这是保罗帮助编写的一项开卷带回家的考试，被一位考生描述为比ABO考试“可能更难”和“更具临床相关性”<ref name="WaPoNBO"/>。保罗任命自己的家庭成员为董事会成员，并将董事会登记到错误的地址<ref name="WaPoNBO"/>。

指定的董事会成员是保罗、他的妻子和他的岳父<ref>{{cite web|date=2010-06-14|title=Rand Paul's Doctor Credentials Questioned for Lacking Top Board's Certification|url=http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2010/06/14/rand-pauls-doctor-credentials-questioned-lacking-boards-certification.html|access-date=2021-07-13|work=Fox News|agency=Associated Press|archive-date=2018-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180510054536/http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2010/06/14/rand-pauls-doctor-credentials-questioned-lacking-boards-certification.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。NBO本身从未被{{le|美国医学专业委员会|American Board of Medical Specialties}}等组织接受为认证实体<ref name="lcj-2010"/>，其认证被许多医院和保险公司视为无效。保罗在2005年让自己的ABO认证失效，这并没有影响他在肯塔基州的执业；该州不要求董事会认证。根据保罗的估计，大约有50或60名医生获得了NBO的认证<ref name="WaPoNBO"/>。NBO成立于1999年，但保罗在2000年没有向肯塔基州州务卿办公室提交所需的文件时允许其解散。 他后来在2005年重新创建了董事会，但在2011年再次解散<ref>{{cite web |title=Certificate of Dissolution |url=https://app.sos.ky.gov/corpscans/24/0479924-09-99999-20111101-ADS-4902880-PU.pdf |website=Kentucky Secretary of State |access-date=2021-07-13 |archive-date=2014-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140823090416/https://app.sos.ky.gov/corpscans/24/0479924-09-99999-20111101-ADS-4902880-PU.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

