保罗被指派到{{le|美国参议院能源和自然资源委员会|United States Senate Committee on Energy and Natural Resources|能源和自然资源委员会}}、{{le|美国参议院健康、教育、劳工和养老金委员会|United States Senate Committee on Health, Education, Labor and Pensions|健康、教育、劳工和养老金委员会}}、{{le|美国参议院国土安全和政府事务委员会|United States Senate Committee on Homeland Security and Governmental Affairs|国土安全和政府事务委员会}}和{{le|美国参议院小企业和创业委员会|United States Senate Committee on Small Business and Entrepreneurship|小企业委员会}}<ref>{{cite news |title=Four committee assignments for Rand Paul |work=Lexington Herald-Leader |date=2011-01-28 |url=http://www.kentucky.com/2011/01/28/1614138/four-committee-assignments-for.html |access-date=2021-01-06 |archive-date=2015-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150414224725/http://www.kentucky.com/2011/01/28/1614138/four-committee-assignments-for.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。保罗还与[[吉姆·德敏特|吉姆·德敏特]]和[[麥克·李_(美國政治家)|迈克·李]]一起成立了{{le|茶党核心小组|Tea Party Caucus|参议院茶党核心小组}}<ref>{{cite news |last=Sonmez |first=Felicia |title=Rand Paul announces Senate Tea Party Caucus |work=The Washington Post |date=2011-01-14 |url=http://voices.washingtonpost.com/44/2011/01/rand-paul-announces-senate-tea.html |access-date=2021-01-06 |archive-date=2020-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806171704/http://voices.washingtonpost.com/44/2011/01/rand-paul-announces-senate-tea.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他的第一个立法提案是在一年内削减5000亿美元的联邦开支。这项提案包括将[[美国教育部|教育部]]削减83%，将[[美国国土安全部|国土安全部]]削减43%，并将[[美国能源部|能源部]]并入[[美国国防部|国防部]]，取消[[美国住房与城市发展部|住房与城市发展部]]。7个独立机构将被取消，食品券将削减30%。根据保罗的提议，国防开支将减少6.5%，[[外援|国际援助]]将被取消<ref>{{cite news |last=Straub |first=Bill |title=Kentucky Sen. Rand Paul rolls out budget ax |work=Evansville Courier & Press |date=2011-01-28 |url=http://www.courierpress.com/news/2011/jan/27/sen-paul-rolls-out-budget-ax/ |access-date=2021-01-06 |archive-date=2012-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120316220522/http://www.courierpress.com/news/2011/jan/27/sen-paul-rolls-out-budget-ax/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Carroll |first=James R. |date=2011-01-25 |title=Senator Rand Paul seeks $500 billion in federal spending cuts |work=The Courier-Journal |location=Louisville, Kentucky |url=https://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/courier_journal/access/2248953991.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Jan+25%2C+2011&author=James+R+Carroll&pub=Courier+-+Journal&edition=&startpage=n%2Fa&desc=Senator+Rand+Paul+seeks+%24500+billion+in+federal+spending+cuts |access-date=2021-01-06 |archive-date=2013-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130727115911/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/courier_journal/access/2248953991.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Jan+25%2C+2011&author=James+R+Carroll&pub=Courier+-+Journal&edition=&startpage=n%2Fa&desc=Senator+Rand+Paul+seeks+%24500+billion+in+federal+spending+cuts |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Freddoso |first=David |date=2011-01-26 |title=A detailed look at the Rand Paul spending bill |work=The Washington Examiner |url=http://washingtonexaminer.com/blogs/beltway-confidential/2011/01/detailed-look-rand-paul-spending-bill |access-date=2021-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110511125605/http://washingtonexaminer.com/blogs/beltway-confidential/2011/01/detailed-look-rand-paul-spending-bill |archive-date=2011-05-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他后来提出了一个旨在平衡预算的五年预算计划<ref>{{cite web |last=Bruce |first=Mary |title=Sen. Paul Unveils 5-Year Budget Plan: Eliminates Four Federal Agencies |website=ABC News |date=2011-03-17 |url=http://blogs.abcnews.com/thenote/2011/03/sen-paul-unveils-5-year-budget-plan-eliminates-four-federal-agencies.html |access-date=2021-01-06 |archive-date=2017-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170803085243/http://blogs.abcnews.com/thenote/2011/03/sen-paul-unveils-5-year-budget-plan-eliminates-four-federal-agencies.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

