保罗表示反对美国干预[[利比亚内战_(2011年)|利比亚内战]]，并批评奥巴马总统的[[奥德赛黎明|奥德赛黎明行动]]没有获得国会的同意<ref>{{cite news |last=Straub |first=Bill |title=Kentucky Senator Paul berates Obama for 'cavalierly taking us to war |work=Evansville Courier & Press |date=2011-03-30 |url=http://www.courierpress.com/news/2011/mar/30/kentucky-senator-paul-berates-obama-cavalierly-tak/ |access-date=2021-01-18 |archive-date=2012-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120316221134/http://www.courierpress.com/news/2011/mar/30/kentucky-senator-paul-berates-obama-cavalierly-tak/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Sonmez |first=Felicia |date=2011-03-17 |title=Rand Paul opposes U.S. military involvement in Libya |work=The Washington Post |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/2chambers/post/rand-paul-opposes-us-military-involvement-in-libya/2011/03/17/ABkw6jl_blog.html |access-date=2021-01-18 |archive-date=2021-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122044415/https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/2chambers/post/rand-paul-opposes-us-military-involvement-in-libya/2011/03/17/ABkw6jl_blog.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[2011年美国债务上限危机|债务上限危机]]期间，保罗表示，只有通过{{le|平衡预算修正案|Balanced budget amendment}}，他才会支持提高债务上限<ref>{{cite web |last=Klein |first=Rick |title=Sen. Rand Paul: No Debt Ceiling Increase Without Balanced Budget Amendment |url=http://blogs.abcnews.com/thenote/2011/06/sen-rand-paul-no-debt-ceiling-increase-without-balanced-budget-amendment.html |website=ABC News |access-date=2021-01-18 |date=2011-06-30 |archive-date=2016-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160405080932/http://blogs.abcnews.com/thenote/2011/06/sen-rand-paul-no-debt-ceiling-increase-without-balanced-budget-amendment.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。保罗是《{{le|削减、限制与平衡法案|Cut, Cap and Balance Act}}》的支持者，该法案由民主党反对派提出<ref>{{cite web |last=Hayward |first=John |title=Cut, Cap, and Balance Killed |url=http://www.humanevents.com/article.php?id=45039 |work=Human Events |access-date=2021-01-18 |date=2011-07-22 }}{{Dead link}}</ref>。8月3日，保罗投票反对提高债务上限的法案<ref>{{cite web |last=Marchmon |first=Jay |title=Rand Paul reacts to passage of debt ceiling bill |url=http://www.wpsdlocal6.com/news/local/Rand-Paul-reacts-to-passage-of-debt-ceiling-bill-126594128.html |website=WPSD-TV |access-date=2021-01-18 |date=2011-08-02 |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111004215912/http://www.wpsdlocal6.com/news/local/Rand-Paul-reacts-to-passage-of-debt-ceiling-bill-126594128.html |archive-date=2011-10-04 }}</ref>。

9月7日，保罗呼吁对[[美国财政部长|美国财政部长]][[蒂莫西·弗朗兹·盖特纳|蒂莫西·盖特纳]]进行不信任投票<ref>{{cite news |last=Hughes |first=Siobhan |title=Rand Paul Calls for No Confidence on Geithner |url=https://blogs.wsj.com/washwire/2011/09/07/rand-paul-calls-for-no-confidence-vote-on-geithner/ |access-date=2021-01-29 |work=The Wall Street Journal |date=2011-09-08 |archive-date=2020-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926090812/https://blogs.wsj.com/washwire/2011/09/07/rand-paul-calls-for-no-confidence-vote-on-geithner/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。当月晚些时候，保罗否决了加强石油和天然气管道安全规则的立法，因为他指出，该法案不够有力<ref>{{cite news |last=Simon |first=Richard |title=Rand Paul blocks pipeline-safety bill, frustrating Californians |url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/nationnow/2011/10/fight-erupts-in-congress-over-pipeline-safety-legislation-.html |access-date=2021-01-29 |work=Los Angeles Times |date=2011-10-05 |archive-date=2017-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170701195622/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/nationnow/2011/10/fight-erupts-in-congress-over-pipeline-safety-legislation-.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。10月，保罗否决了一项提供3600万美元援助的法案，他说，他担心这可能被用来援助国内恐怖分子。这是对两名通过一项难民计划来到美国的恐怖分子的回应，2011年，他们在保罗的家乡[[鲍灵格林_(肯塔基州)|鲍灵格林]]被捕<ref>{{cite web |last=Wong |first=Scott |title=Rand Paul blocking refugee funds |url=http://www.politico.com/news/stories/1011/65142.html |access-date=2021-01-29 |work=Politico |date=2011-10-05 |archive-date=2014-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140823090346/http://www.politico.com/news/stories/1011/65142.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在民主党领导人承诺举行一次国会听证会，讨论如何挑选个人获得难民身份，并要求调查这两名嫌疑人是如何通过难民计划被接纳入境的之后，保罗解除了对该法案的控制<ref>{{cite web |last=Wong |first=Scott |title=Rand Paul ends hold on SSI benefits |url=http://www.politico.com/news/stories/1011/65142.html |access-date=2021-01-29 |work=Politico |date=2011-10-17 |archive-date=2014-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140823090346/http://www.politico.com/news/stories/1011/65142.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年6月，保罗支持[[米特·罗姆尼|米特·罗姆尼]]，因为很明显他将成为[[2012年美国总统选举|2012年总统选举]]的共和党候选人<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.politico.com/blogs/burns-haberman/2012/06/rand-paul-endorses-romney-125624 |title=Rand Paul endorses Romney |first=Alexander |last=Burns |date=2012-06-07 |website=Politico |accessdate=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2017-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170629183227/http://www.politico.com/blogs/burns-haberman/2012/06/rand-paul-endorses-romney-125624 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。不过他后来公开表示他与罗姆尼在一些政策上的分歧<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cnn.com/2012/10/10/opinion/rand-paul-romney-foreign-policy/ |title=Rand Paul: Romney's wrong on Middle East, defense spending |author=Paul, Rand |date=2012-10-10 |website=CNN |access-date=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2017-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107222500/http://www.cnn.com/2012/10/10/opinion/rand-paul-romney-foreign-policy/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===第113届国会（2013－2015年）===
在第113届国会中，保罗被分配到[[美国参议院外交委员会|外交关系委员会]]，并在卫生、教育、劳工和养老金、国土安全和政府事务以及小企业委员会中留任。<ref>{{cite web |last=McCarthy |first=Daniel |title=Rand Paul on the Foreign Relations Committee – and What It Means |url=http://www.theamericanconservative.com/rand-paul-on-foreign-relations-committee/ |work=The American Conservative |access-date=2021-01-29 |date=2013-01-03 |archive-date=2014-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140823090436/http://www.theamericanconservative.com/rand-paul-on-foreign-relations-committee/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2013年3月6日至7日，保罗参与了一场{{le|美国参议院的冗长演说|Filibuster in the United States Senate|冗长演说}}，以推迟对[[约翰·歐文·布伦南|约翰·布伦南]]担任中央情报局局长的提名投票。保罗质疑{{le|巴拉克·奥巴马内阁|Presidency of Barack Obama|奥巴马政府}}使用[[无人航空载具|无人机]]的行为，以及在美国境内使用无人机的法律依据。保罗在会上发言了12小时52分钟<ref>{{cite web |title=Rand Paul Ends Epic Mr. Smith-Style Filibuster After More Than 12 Hours |url=http://www.slate.com/blogs/the_slatest/2013/03/06/rand_paul_is_waging_an_epic_mr_smith_style_filibuster_right_now.html |first=Josh |last=Voorhees |work=Slate |access-date=2021-01-29 |date=2013-03-07 |archive-date=2021-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105064544/https://slate.com/news-and-politics/2013/03/rand-paul-is-waging-an-epic-mr-smith-style-filibuster-right-now.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他让位给了几位共和党参议员和民主党参议员[[罗恩·怀登|罗恩·怀登]]，后者也经常对无人机的使用提出质疑<ref>{{cite web |title=Sen. Paul holds floor for hours in filibuster of CIA nominee, over drone concerns |url=http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2013/03/06/sen-paul-holds-floor-for-hours-in-filibuster-cia-nominee-over-drone-concerns/ |website=Fox News |date=2013-03-06 |access-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130307032926/http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2013/03/06/sen-paul-holds-floor-for-hours-in-filibuster-cia-nominee-over-drone-concerns/ |archive-date=2013-03-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Ewing |first=Philip |title=Rand Paul pulls plug on nearly 13-hour filibuster on drones |url=http://www.politico.com/story/2013/03/rand-paul-filibuster-john-brennan-cia-nominee-88507.html |work=Politico |access-date=2021-01-29 |date=2013-03-06 |archive-date=2015-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618115938/http://www.politico.com/story/2013/03/rand-paul-filibuster-john-brennan-cia-nominee-88507.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。保罗说，他的目的是对无人机政策提出总体上的挑战，特别是因为它涉及美国本土的非战斗人员。他要求政府保证非战斗人员不会成为美国本土的目标<ref>{{cite news |last=Michaels |first=Jim |title=Rand Paul ends epic filibuster over Brennan |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2013/03/07/rand-paul-brennan-filibuster/1969869/ |work=USA Today |access-date=2021-01-29 |date=2013-03-07 |archive-date=2020-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105113619/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2013/03/07/rand-paul-brennan-filibuster/1969869/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。司法部长[[埃里克·霍尔德|埃里克·霍尔德]]回应说，总统无权在没有正当程序的情况下对非战斗人员公民实施{{le|法外惩罚|Extrajudicial punishment}}。新闻秘书[[杰伊·卡尼|杰伊·卡尼]]读了霍尔德的信，信中表示[[奥巴马总统|奥巴马总统]]的支持，“总统没有也不会对美国本土的美国公民使用无人机袭击”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://obamawhitehouse.archives.gov/the-press-office/2013/03/07/press-briefing-press-secretary-jay-carney-372013|title=Press briefing — secretary Carney 3/7/2013|date=2013-03-07|accessdate=2021-01-29|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128155630/https://obamawhitehouse.archives.gov/the-press-office/2013/03/07/press-briefing-press-secretary-jay-carney-372013|dead-url=no}}</ref>。保罗回答说，他对霍尔德的回答“相当满意”<ref>{{cite news |title=Rand Paul 'happy' with drone response |url=http://politicalticker.blogs.cnn.com/2013/03/07/obama-administration-responds-to-paul-on-drones/ |website=CNN |access-date=2021-01-29 |date=2013-03-03 |archive-date=2017-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170707051112/http://politicalticker.blogs.cnn.com/2013/03/07/obama-administration-responds-to-paul-on-drones/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。冗长演说以81票对16票[[辩论终结|结束]]，布伦南以63票对34票获得参议院的确认<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/03/08/us/politics/brennan-confirmed-to-lead-the-cia.html |title=Brennan Confirmed to Lead the C.I.A. |first=Sarah |last=Wheaton |date=2013-03-07 |newspaper=The New York Times |access-date=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2017-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170130144934/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/03/08/us/politics/brennan-confirmed-to-lead-the-cia.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

