===第115届国会（2017－2019年）===
2017年3月，保罗提出了《{{le|停止武装恐怖分子法案|Stop Arming Terrorists Act}}》，该法禁止使用美国政府资金向[[基地组织|基地组织]]、[[征服沙姆阵线|征服沙姆阵线]]、[[伊拉克和黎凡特伊斯兰国|伊拉克和黎凡特伊斯兰国]]以及支持这些组织的国家提供援助<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.congress.gov/bill/115th-congress/house-bill/608/all-info |title=All Information (Except Text) for H.R.608 - Stop Arming Terrorists Act |website=U.S. Congress |access-date=2021-03-09 |archive-date=2021-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110083707/https://www.congress.gov/bill/115th-congress/house-bill/608/all-info |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/the-two-non-interventionists_us_594f1cdde4b0326c0a8d0918 |title=The Two Non-Interventionists |first=Nathan |last=Thomas |date=2017-07-03 |website=HuffPost |access-date=2021-03-09 |archive-date=2019-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190209201720/https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/the-two-non-interventionists_us_594f1cdde4b0326c0a8d0918 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。3月16日，参议员[[约翰·麦凯恩|约翰·麦凯恩]]指责保罗是[[弗拉基米尔·普京|弗拉基米尔·普京]]的代理人，因为保罗反对将[[黑山|黑山]]加入[[北约|北约]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://insider.foxnews.com/2017/03/15/john-mccain-accuses-rand-paul-working-vladimir-putin-and-russia-over-montenegro |title=John McCain: Rand Paul 'Now Working for Vladimir Putin' |website=Fox News |date=2017-03-15 |access-date=2021-03-09 |archive-date=2017-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170703185223/http://insider.foxnews.com/2017/03/15/john-mccain-accuses-rand-paul-working-vladimir-putin-and-russia-over-montenegro |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.yahoo.com/news/john-mccain-accuses-rand-paul-170938509.html |title=John McCain accuses Rand Paul of working for Vladimir Putin |website=Yahoo! News |date=2017-03-16 |access-date=2021-03-09 |archive-date=2017-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170506110720/https://www.yahoo.com/news/john-mccain-accuses-rand-paul-170938509.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第二天，保罗回应说，麦凯恩“提出了一个非常、非常有力的任期限制理由”，暗示麦凯恩由于资历的原因变得“有点精神错乱”<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/onpolitics/2017/03/16/rand-paul-and-john-mccain-trade-jabs-paul-calls-mccain-past-his-prime-unhinged/99271966/ |title=Rand Paul and John McCain trade jabs, as Paul calls McCain 'past his prime,' 'unhinged' |date=2017-03-16 |newspaper=USA Today |first=Eliza |last=Collins |accessdate=2021-03-09 |archive-date=2020-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806144029/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/onpolitics/2017/03/16/rand-paul-and-john-mccain-trade-jabs-paul-calls-mccain-past-his-prime-unhinged/99271966/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。4月7日，麦凯恩说，他没有关注保罗的任何言辞，后者在美国参议院没有“任何真正的影响力”<ref>{{cite magazine |url=http://time.com/4731909/donald-trump-jose-andres/ |title=John McCain Slams Rand Paul Over Syria: 'He Doesn't Have Any Real Influence' |date=2017-04-07 |magazine=TIME |accessdate=2021-03-09 |archive-date=2017-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170430190843/http://time.com/4731909/donald-trump-jose-andres/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

保罗质疑特朗普总统[[2017年沙伊拉特打击行动|2017年4月对叙利亚的导弹袭击]]，他说，“虽然我们都谴责叙利亚的暴行，但美国没有受到攻击。”他说，未经国会授权，不应采取进一步行动。<ref>{{cite web |last1=King |first1=Alexandra |title=Rand Paul: Syria strikes 'not in the national interest' |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2017/04/08/politics/rand-paul-smercinish-cnntv |access-date=2021-03-09 |work=CNN |date=2017-04-08 |archive-date=2021-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224224435/https://edition.cnn.com/2017/04/08/politics/rand-paul-smercinish-cnntv |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Lardner |first1=Richard |title=Lawmakers slam Trump for bypassing Congress on Syria strike |url=https://www.boston.com/news/politics/2017/04/07/lawmakers-slam-trump-for-bypassing-congress-on-syria-strike |access-date=2021-03-09 |work=Boston.com |agency=Associated Press |date=2017-04-07 |archive-date=2017-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170612045739/https://www.boston.com/news/politics/2017/04/07/lawmakers-slam-trump-for-bypassing-congress-on-syria-strike |dead-url=no }}</ref>

22位参议员给总统[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]递交联名信，保罗便是在信上签字的参议员之一<ref>{{cite web |last1=Inhofe |first1=James |last2=Paul |first2=Rand |display-authors=etal |title=Letter to the Honorable Donald J. Trump |date=2017-05-27 |url=https://www.inhofe.senate.gov/download/?id=E1E34574-5655-42AA-92E8-0D23DC8C33BA&download=1 |website=James M. Inhofe, U.S. Senator for Oklahoma |access-date=2021-03-09 |archive-date=2017-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170606005302/https://www.inhofe.senate.gov/download/?id=E1E34574-5655-42AA-92E8-0D23DC8C33BA&download=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他敦促总统在2017年5月让美国退出《[[巴黎协定|巴黎协定]]》。根据{{le|政治反应中心|Center for Responsive Politics}}的数据，自2012年以来，保罗已经从石油、天然气和煤炭权益中获得了超过25万美元的收益<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2017/jun/01/republican-senators-paris-climate-deal-energy-donations|access-date=2017-06-01|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2017-06-01|title=The Republicans who urged Trump to pull out of Paris deal are big oil darlings|first1=Tom|last1=McCarthy|first2=Lauren|last2=Gambino|archive-date=2017-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170601120951/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2017/jun/01/republican-senators-paris-climate-deal-energy-donations|dead-url=no}}</ref>。7月，兰德保罗加入了众议员[[贾斯汀·阿马什|贾斯汀·阿马什]]（R-MI）、[[托马斯·马西|托马斯·马西]]（R-KY）、[[吉米·邓肯|吉米·邓肯]]（R-TN）和参议员[[伯尼·桑德斯|伯尼·桑德斯]]（I-VT）反对对[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]、[[伊朗|伊朗]]和[[朝鲜|朝鲜]]实施新的经济制裁的法案。总统特朗普亦反对该法案，指出与俄罗斯的关系已经处于“历史上最危险的低点”。不过，他确实签署了这项法案，尽管可能是出于政治压力。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://ivn.us/2017/08/03/meet-5-lawmakers-voted-against-russia-sanctions-bill/ |title=Meet the 5 Lawmakers Who Voted Against the Russia Sanctions Bill |first=Thomas A. |last=Hawk |date=2017-08-03 |website=Independent Voter News |accessdate=2021-03-09 |archive-date=2017-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806023041/https://ivn.us/2017/08/03/meet-5-lawmakers-voted-against-russia-sanctions-bill/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

9月5日，特朗普政府宣布有意撤销[[童年入境者暂缓遣返手续|童年入境者暂缓遣返手续]]（DACA）。保罗在推特上回应该法案时表示，创建DACA的行政命令是非法的，需要国会两党合作来解决或修复该程序。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://thehill.com/homenews/administration/349219-rand-paul-calls-for-bipartisan-daca-solution |title=Paul calls for bipartisan DACA solution |first=Olivia |last=Beavers |date=2017-09-05 |newspaper=The Hill |accessdate=2021-04-04 |archive-date=2021-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122135832/https://thehill.com/homenews/administration/349219-rand-paul-calls-for-bipartisan-daca-solution |dead-url=no }}</ref>

保罗在2017年10月的一次采访中证实，除非将数十亿美元的开支从计划中删除，否则他不会投票赞成参议院的共和党预算案：“如果领导层不愿意与担心债务的人妥协，那么他们就应该输掉。”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.politico.com/story/2017/10/17/rand-paul-oppose-senate-gop-budget-243864 |first1=Burgess |last1=Everett |first2=Seung Min |last2=Kim |title=Rand Paul opposes Senate GOP budget |date=2017-10-17 |website=Politico |accessdate=2021-04-04 |archive-date=2021-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118013333/https://www.politico.com/story/2017/10/17/rand-paul-oppose-senate-gop-budget-243864 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2018年2月，共和党参议员提出了类似于特朗普总统提议的移民框架，并在他的支持下呼吁为边境安全提供250亿美元，以换取180万非法入境美国的公民身份<ref>{{cite news |url=http://thehill.com/homenews/senate/373514-gop-senators-introduce-trump-immigration-framework |title=GOP senators introduce Trump immigration framework |date=2018-02-12 |accessdate=2021-04-04 |newspaper=The Hill |first=Jordain |last=Carney |archive-date=2021-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122141405/https://thehill.com/homenews/senate/373514-gop-senators-introduce-trump-immigration-framework |dead-url=no }}</ref>。保罗是投票反对该提案的14名共和党参议员之一<ref>{{cite news |url=http://thehill.com/homenews/senate/374321-the-14-gop-senators-who-voted-against-trumps-immigration-framework |title=The 14 GOP senators who voted against Trump's immigration framework |first=Jordain |last=Carney |newspaper=The Hill |date=2018-02-17 |accessdate=2021-04-04 |archive-date=2021-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210613190754/https://thehill.com/homenews/senate/374321-the-14-gop-senators-who-voted-against-trumps-immigration-framework |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

跟踪国会投票情况的[[FiveThirtyEight|FiveThirtyEight]]发现，保罗与唐纳德·特朗普立场相同投票的次数在所有共和党人中最少，截至2018年8月，只有74%的时间与他一起投票<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://projects.fivethirtyeight.com/congress-trump-score/rand-paul/ |title=Tracking Congress In The Age Of Trump |last=Bycoffe |first=Aaron |date=2017-01-30 |work=FiveThirtyEight |access-date=2021-04-04 |archive-date=2018-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181201135329/https://projects.fivethirtyeight.com/congress-trump-score/rand-paul/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2018年12月，在法庭提交文件暗示特朗普总统参与竞选资金违规，包括试图收买一名女性的沉默之后，保罗淡化了涉嫌的违规行为，并表示不应“过度定罪”<ref name="legal-storm">{{Cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/republicans-defend-trump-amid-brewing-legal-storm/2018/12/09/a3e7a496-fbc6-11e8-ad40-cdfd0e0dd65a_story.html |title=Republicans defend Trump amid brewing legal storm |last1=Sonmez |first1=Felicia |last2=Cha |first2=Ariana Eunjung |date=2018-12-09 |newspaper=The Washington Post |access-date=2021-04-04 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121152929/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/republicans-defend-trump-amid-brewing-legal-storm/2018/12/09/a3e7a496-fbc6-11e8-ad40-cdfd0e0dd65a_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。保罗说，竞选资金违规是“在提交文件或不分类方面的一个错误”，追查这些违规行为将把美国变成一个“[[香蕉共和国|香蕉共和国]]——在那里，每一位总统都会被起诉，每一位总统都会在任期结束后被投入监狱。”<ref name="legal-storm" />

===第116届国会（2019－2021年）===
2019年1月，保罗谴责参议员[[米特·罗姆尼|米特·罗姆尼]]撰写社论批评特朗普总统。保罗说，罗姆尼对特朗普性格的批评对国家和共和党都不利。<ref name="RipsRomney">{{Cite web |url=https://politi.co/2BW7gWx |title=Rand Paul rips Romney for criticizing Trump |last=Everett |first=Burgess |website=Politico |language=en |access-date=2020-12-31 |archive-date=2021-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105064606/https://www.politico.com/story/2019/01/02/rand-paul-romney-trump-criticism-1077570 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2019年7月17日，保罗与犹他州参议员[[麥克·李_(美國政治家)|迈克·李]]一起，阻止了参议员[[陆天娜|柯尔斯滕·吉利布兰德]]就延长{{le|9·11受害者赔偿基金|September 11th Victim Compensation Fund}}的法案获得{{le|一致同意|Unanimous consent}}的动议。估计该基金在年底将用完。保罗辩称，他并不是在阻挠这项法案，而是在寻求就另一项修正案进行表决，该修正案将通过其他因赤字而削减的开支来抵消新的开支。喜剧演员[[乔恩·斯图尔特|乔恩·斯图尔特]]和9·11事件的第一反应者{{le|约翰·费尔|John Feal}}在[[福克斯新闻|福克斯新闻]]上的一段话中，指责保罗“财政责任{{le|美德信号|Virtue signalling}}”虚伪，拖延了法案的通过，同时他投票赞成[[2017年减税与就业法案|2017年减税与就业法案]]，该法案增加了赤字<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/nation/2019/07/18/jon-stewart-rand-paul-mike-lee-victims-fund-delay/ |title=Jon Stewart accuses Rand Paul of 'fiscal responsibility virtue signaling' in stalling 9/11 victims funding |first=Allyson |last=Chiu |date=2019-07-18 |newspaper=The Washington Post |access-date=2020-12-31 |archive-date=2019-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206125325/https://www.washingtonpost.com/nation/2019/07/18/jon-stewart-rand-paul-mike-lee-victims-fund-delay/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。保罗说，他一直坚持“{{le|即付即用条款|PAYGO}}”，以增加包括用于救灾资金的支出，并称斯图尔特不知情，是“左翼暴徒”的一部分<ref>{{cite web |last1=Wise |first1=Justin |title=Rand Paul accuses Jon Stewart of being 'part of left-wing mob' after criticism over 9/11 victim fund |url=https://thehill.com/homenews/senate/453823-rand-paul-accuses-jon-stewart-of-being-part-of-left-wing-mob-after-criticism |website=[[The_Hill_(newspaper)|The Hill]] |accessdate=2020-12-31 |date=2019-07-18 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108002014/https://thehill.com/homenews/senate/453823-rand-paul-accuses-jon-stewart-of-being-part-of-left-wing-mob-after-criticism |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

