===背景===
[[File:Rand_Paul_by_Gage_Skidmore_7.jpg|right]]{{le|国家港 (马里兰州)|National Harbor, Maryland|国家港}}举行的2013年[[保守政治行动会议|保守政治行动会议]]（CPAC）上发表讲话。]]
[[File:Rand_Paul_(22525600570).jpg|thumb]][[得梅因|得梅因]]的竞选集会上讲话]]
至少从2013年1月起，保罗就被认为是[[2016年美国总统选举共和党初选|共和党提名]][[美国总统|美国总统]]的潜在候选人<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.politico.com/story/2013/01/rand-paul-gop-must-evolve-and-adapt-86473.html |title=Rand Paul: GOP must evolve, adapt |first=Mackenzie |last=Weinger |work=Politico |date=2013-01-28 |access-date=2021-04-16 |archive-date=2015-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150717132825/http://www.politico.com/story/2013/01/rand-paul-gop-must-evolve-and-adapt-86473.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他在2013年2月13日对[[贝拉克·奥巴马|总统奥巴马]]的{{le|2013年国情咨文|2013 State of the Union Address|国情咨文}}发表了茶党的回应<ref name="rebuttal">{{cite web |url=http://www.politico.com/story/2013/02/tea-party-rebuttal-text-of-rand-paul-response-87557.html |title=Tea party State of the Union 2013 rebuttal: Rand Paul response (full text) |work=Politico |date=2013-02-13 |access-date=2021-04-16 |archive-date=2014-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140823090211/http://www.politico.com/story/2013/02/tea-party-rebuttal-text-of-rand-paul-response-87557.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而[[马可·鲁比奥|马可·鲁比奥]]则给出了共和党的官方回应。这促使一些权威人士将这一天称为2016年共和党初选的开始<ref>{{Cite web|title=Rand Paul: 'Big Government's Not A Friend To Those Who Are Trying To Get Ahead'|url=https://www.npr.org/2013/02/14/172034468/rand-paul-big-governments-not-a-friend-to-those-who-are-trying-to-get-ahead|website=NPR|date=2013-02-14|accessdate=2021-04-16|archive-date=2021-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210419230957/https://www.npr.org/2013/02/14/172034468/rand-paul-big-governments-not-a-friend-to-those-who-are-trying-to-get-ahead|dead-url=no}}</ref>。那一年，保罗在[[华盛顿特区|华盛顿特区]]举行的[[保守政治行动会议|保守政治行动会议]]（CPAC）上发表讲话，赢得2016年总统非正式民意测验。保罗在接下来的两年里也赢得了非正式民意测验的支持，这使得一些人认为保罗是候选人提名的领跑者，尽管参加CPAC的人通常被认为比普通共和党选民更年轻、更具自由意志态度。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2015/02/28/rand-paul-wins-2015-cpac-straw-poll |title=Rand Paul wins 2015 CPAC straw poll |website=Fox News |access-date=2021-04-16 |date=2015-02-28 |archive-date=2015-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151025174725/http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2015/02/28/rand-paul-wins-2015-cpac-straw-poll/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Rand Paul wins CPAC straw poll, with Scott Walker a close second |newspaper=The Washington Post |date=2015-02-28 |last=Cha |first=Ariana |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/post-politics/wp/2015/02/28/rand-paul-wins-cpac-straw-poll-narrowly-topping-walker |access-date=2021-04-16 |quote=A candidate's popularity with the Conservative Political Action Conference hasn't necessarily been a great predictor of his or her success with the larger GOP electorate, as attendees tend to have a stronger libertarian bent than the Republican majority. |archive-date=2015-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150721215244/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/post-politics/wp/2015/02/28/rand-paul-wins-cpac-straw-poll-narrowly-topping-walker/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Senator Rand Paul wins straw poll in boost to 2016 presidential prospects |website=Reuters |date=2015-02-28 |last=Holland |first=Steve |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/01/us-randpaul-idUSKBN0LW0YY20150301 |access-date=2021-04-16 |quote=Whether the victory for Paul will have long-lasting benefit is unclear since his libertarian views may not have broad appeal in the Republican Party. |archive-date=2015-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150302031228/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/01/us-randpaul-idUSKBN0LW0YY20150301 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

在2014年4月共和党自由峰会上的一次演讲中，保罗坚持共和党必须扩大其吸引力，才能成为一个政党。他说，要做到这一点，它不可能是一个“大亨、富人和华尔街”的政党，保守派运动从来就不是关于富人或特权的，“我们是中产阶级”。保罗还说，保守主义者必须向失业者传达正义和关心的信息，并反对政府的监视，以吸引新人加入这场运动，包括年轻人、西班牙裔和黑人。<ref>{{cite web |title=Obamacare' under attack as conservatives eye 2016 |url=https://news.yahoo.com/obamacare-under-attack-conservatives-eye-2016-200658669--election.html |agency=Associated Press |website=Yahoo! News |author=Peoples, Steve |access-date=2021-04-16 |archive-date=2016-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401091254/http://news.yahoo.com/obamacare-under-attack-conservatives-eye-2016-200658669--election.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2014年大选期间，保罗发起了一场名为“希拉里的失败者”的社交媒体宣传活动，意在突出许多民主党候选人尽管获得[[希拉里·克林顿|希拉里·克林顿]]的支持，但仍在竞选美国参议院时落败。希拉里·克林顿也是[[2016年希拉里·克林顿竞选美国总统|总统候选人]]，最终赢得{{le|2016年美国总统选举民主党初选|2016 Democratic Party presidential primaries|民主党提名}}，在[[2016年美国总统选举|大选]]中输给[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2014/nov/7/rand-paul-clinton-democrats-became-hillarys-losers |title=Rand Paul: 'Clinton Democrats' became 'Hillary's losers' during election landslide |newspaper=Washington Times |access-date=2021-04-16 |date=2014-11-07 |last=Sherfinski |first=David |archive-date=2021-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210419020129/https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2014/nov/7/rand-paul-clinton-democrats-became-hillarys-losers/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

保罗于2015年初开始组建竞选团队，设立竞选办公室，并聘请竞选经理，这引发了人们对他准备参加总统竞选的猜测<ref name="hires">{{cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/post-politics/wp/2015/01/13/rand-paul-announces-campaign-manager-as-he-ramps-up-2016-campaign |title=Rand Paul announces campaign manager for likely 2016 campaign |date=2015-01-13 |work=The Washington Post |last=Costa |first=Robert |accessdate=2021-04-16 |archive-date=2015-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150707235220/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/post-politics/wp/2015/01/13/rand-paul-announces-campaign-manager-as-he-ramps-up-2016-campaign/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。保罗于2015年4月7日正式宣布参选总统。在他宣布当天，保罗筹集了100万美元<ref>{{cite news |last1=Ballhaus |first1=Rebecca |title=Rand Paul Sprints to $1 Million Fundraising Mark |url=https://blogs.wsj.com/washwire/2015/04/08/rand-paul-sprints-to-1-million-fundraising-mark/ |work=The Wall Street Journal |date=2015-04-08 |accessdate=2021-04-16 |archive-date=2021-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117191107/https://blogs.wsj.com/washwire/2015/04/08/rand-paul-sprints-to-1-million-fundraising-mark/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

