|title=Ron Paul's son borrows tactics for Senate bid in Kentucky |url=http://www.courierpress.com/news/2009/nov/11/ron-pauls-son-borrows-tactics-senate-bid-kentucky/ |newspaper=Evansville Courier & Press |location=Evansville, IN |date=2009-11-11 |accessdate=2020-12-29 |agency=Associated Press |archive-date=2013-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101135222/http://www.courierpress.com/news/2009/nov/11/ron-pauls-son-borrows-tactics-senate-bid-kentucky/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。自2010年以来，他曾表示，他将允许医生在[[子宫外孕|子宫外孕]]等危及生命的情况下有自由裁量权<ref name="prolifeaw">{{cite web |last=Abad-Santos |first=Alexander |title=Rand Paul isn't 100% pro life anymore |url=http://www.theatlanticwire.com/politics/2013/03/rand-paul-isnt-100-pro-life-any-more/63324/ |newspaper=The Atlantic Wire |date=2013-03-20 |access-date=2020-12-29 |archive-date=2013-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131030201053/http://www.theatlanticwire.com/politics/2013/03/rand-paul-isnt-100-pro-life-any-more/63324/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2011年，保罗签署了{{le|不要纳税人资助堕胎法案|No Taxpayer Funding for Abortion}}，该法案旨在禁止联邦资助堕胎，但强奸、乱伦和拯救母亲生命的堕胎除外<ref>{{cite web|date=2011-01-20|title=H.R.3 - No Taxpayer Funding for Abortion Act|url=https://www.congress.gov/bill/112th-congress/house-bill/3|website=Congress.gov|access-date=2020-12-29|archive-date=2020-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210203052/https://www.congress.gov/bill/112th-congress/house-bill/3|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===移民===
2017年，在特朗普总统决定废除前一届奥巴马政府的[[童年入境者暂缓遣返手续|童年入境者暂缓遣返手续]]（DACA）后，保罗概述了他自己解决无证移民问题的方法，其中包括将DACA受益人入籍五年，作为年度移民配额的一部分，同时也为无证移民提供了一条获得公民身份的途径。保罗说，他反对在边境上的总开支，并同情大多数移民，不管他们的身份如何，尤其是DACA的受益者。<ref>{{cite web|last=Paul|first=Rand|title=Rand Paul on Donald Trump's DACA Decision|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JIgzjE_jfsY|website=YouTube|date=2017-09-11|access-date=2020-12-30|archive-date=2017-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170915134229/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JIgzjE_jfsY&gl=US&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>

保罗是2019年投票反对特朗普“紧急边境资金”要求的11名共和党人之一。<ref>{{cite news|title=11 Senate Republicans voted to block Trump's border wall emergency declaration|url=https://www.vox.com/2019/9/25/20880248/senate-republicans-trump-border-wall|website=Vox|date=2019-09-25|access-date=2020-12-30|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204180713/https://www.vox.com/2019/9/25/20880248/senate-republicans-trump-border-wall|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===同性婚姻===
保罗曾说，[[同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]在个人层面上“冒犯了他自己和很多人”，并说“存在一种危机，让人们认为会有其他类型的婚姻。”<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/08/us/politics/rand-paul-on-the-issues.html |title=Rand Paul on the Issues |work=The New York Times |date=2015-04-07 |access-date=2020-12-29 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112024851/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/08/us/politics/rand-paul-on-the-issues.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Boaz>{{cite web |url=http://www.newsweek.com/rand-paul-real-libertarian-319959 |title=Is Rand Paul a Real Libertarian? |work=Newsweek |date=2015-04-06 |last=Boaz |first=David |access-date=2020-12-29 |quote=His recent comments on gay marriage—"personally offended" and "moral crisis"—created a libertarian backlash. |archive-date=2021-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210219071244/https://www.newsweek.com/rand-paul-real-libertarian-319959 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在[[美国最高法院|最高法院]]2015年对[[奥贝格费尔诉霍奇斯案|奥贝格费尔诉霍奇斯案]]案作出裁决，使美国各地的同性婚姻合法化之前，保罗认为，禁止同性婚姻的决定应该由{{le|美国州政府|State governments of the United States|各州}}来决定<ref name=NYTKentucky>{{cite news |last=Urbina |first=Ian |date=2009-11-25 |title=In Kentucky, a Senate Candidate With a Pedigree for Agitation |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/11/26/us/politics/26kentucky.html |newspaper=The New York Times |location=New York |access-date=2020-12-29 |archive-date=2019-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190602162902/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/11/26/us/politics/26kentucky.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在法院作出决定后，保罗在2015年称“虽然我不同意最高法院对婚姻的重新定义，但我相信所有美国人都有权订立合同。宪法对婚姻问题保持沉默，因为婚姻一直是一个地方性问题。我们的开国元勋是去当地法院结婚的，而不是去华盛顿特区。我经常说我不想让我的枪或我的婚姻在华盛顿登记。”<ref>{{cite news|last=Paul|first=Rand|date=2015-06-28|title=Rand Paul: Government Should Get Out of the Marriage Business Altogether|url=https://time.com/3939374/rand-paul-gay-marriage-supreme-court/|newspaper=Time|access-date=2020-12-29|archive-date=2021-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213215344/https://time.com/3939374/rand-paul-gay-marriage-supreme-court/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===对外政策===
与他更为强硬的“不干涉主义”父亲不同，保罗承认美国海外武装部队的角色，包括永久性的外国军事基地<ref>{{cite web |last=Ward |first=Jon |url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/04/01/rand-paul-military-bases_n_2981368.html |title=Rand Paul Supports Some Military Bases On Foreign Soil, A Big Difference From His Dad |work=The Huffington Post |date=2013-04-01 |access-date=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2017-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170908003012/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/04/01/rand-paul-military-bases_n_2981368.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他曾说，他指责[[伊拉克战争|伊拉克战争]]的支持者而不是奥巴马总统导致2014年暴力的增长，伊拉克战争“鼓舞”了伊朗<ref>{{cite web |title=Rand Paul: Blame Bush, Not Obama |url=http://www.nationalreview.com/corner/380933/rand-paul-blame-bush-not-obama-eliana-johnson |work=National Review |access-date=2020-12-30 |last=Johnson |first=Eliana |date=2014-06-22 |archive-date=2017-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170327165752/http://www.nationalreview.com/corner/380933/rand-paul-blame-bush-not-obama-eliana-johnson |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[迪克·切尼|迪克·切尼]]、[[约翰·麦凯恩|约翰·麦凯恩]]和[[里克·佩里|里克·佩里]]回应称保罗是[[孤立主义|孤立主义]]者<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/rand-paul-blame-dick-cheney-for-iraq-violence-not-president-obama |title=Rand Paul: Blame Dick Cheney for Iraq violence, not Obama |last1=Miller |first1=Jake |date=2014-06-22 |website=CBS News |access-date=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2020-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218210654/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/rand-paul-blame-dick-cheney-for-iraq-violence-not-president-obama/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://m.washingtonpost.com/opinions/rick-perry-isolationist-policies-make-the-threat-of-terrorism-even-greater/2014/07/11/6dbfba4a-06f0-11e4-bbf1-cc51275e7f8f_story.html |title=Isolationist policies make the threat of terrorism even greater |last1=Perry |first1=Rick |date=2014-07-11 |work=The Washington Post |access-date=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2021-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105064643/https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/rick-perry-isolationist-policies-make-the-threat-of-terrorism-even-greater/2014/07/11/6dbfba4a-06f0-11e4-bbf1-cc51275e7f8f_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但保罗指出，对可能的共和党初选选民进行的民意调查支持他的立场<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.defensenews.com/article/20140711/CONGRESSWATCH/307140012 |title=GOP's Paul Doubles Down on Isolationism |last1=Bennett |first1=John T. |date=2014-07-11 |website=DefenseNews.com |access-date=2020-12-30 }}{{Dead link}}</ref>。2011年，保罗当选后不久，提出了一项预算，其中明确规定了5420亿美元的国防开支。2015年，他呼吁国防预算达到6970亿美元<ref>{{cite magazine |url=http://time.com/3759378/rand-paul-defense-spending |title=Rand Paul Proposes Boosting Defense Spending |last1=Rogers |first1=Alex |date=2015-03-26 |magazine=TIME |access-date=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2021-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201222350/https://time.com/3759378/rand-paul-defense-spending/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===大麻===
关于{{le|美国非医用大麻的非犯罪化|Decriminalization of non-medical cannabis in the United States|大麻合法化}}，保罗说这个问题应该交给各州来解决，“只要你不伤害别人，你应该可以做你想做的事”。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Skye |first1=Dan |title=The High Times Interview: Rand Paul |url=https://hightimes.com/news/legalization/the-high-times-interview-rand-paul/ |accessdate=2020-12-30 |work=High Times |date=2015-10-14 |archive-date=2020-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927173122/https://hightimes.com/news/legalization/the-high-times-interview-rand-paul/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Price |first1=Autumn |title=Rand Paul goes into detail with Stephen Colbert on how the drug war unfairly targets "black and brown" people |url=https://rare.us/rare-politics/rare-liberty/war-on-drugs-rare-liberty/rand-paul-goes-into-detail-with-stephen-colbert-on-how-the-drug-war-unfairly-targets-black-and-brown-people/ |accessdate=2020-12-30 |work=Rare |date=2018-02-01 |archive-date=2020-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114120946/https://rare.us/rare-politics/rare-liberty/war-on-drugs-rare-liberty/rand-paul-goes-into-detail-with-stephen-colbert-on-how-the-drug-war-unfairly-targets-black-and-brown-people/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>关于{{le|美国的医用大麻|Medical cannabis in the United States|医疗用途}}，保罗支持肯塔基州的合法化努力<ref>{{cite web |title=Senator Rand Paul shows support for medical marijuana bill |url=https://www.wkyt.com/content/news/Senator-Rand-Paul-shows-support-for-medical-marijuana-bill--476398413.html |accessdate=2020-12-30 |work=WKYT |date=2018-03-09 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109024950/https://www.wkyt.com/content/news/Senator-Rand-Paul-shows-support-for-medical-marijuana-bill--476398413.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并在2015年引入了《{{le|美国大麻立法建议|Cannabis legislation proposals in the United States|照料者法案}}》，以使联邦层面医疗大麻合法化<ref>{{cite press release |date=2015-03-10 |title=Sens. Paul, Booker, & Gillibrand Announce CARERS Act |url=https://www.paul.senate.gov/news/sens-paul-booker-gillibrand-announce-carers-act |location=Washington, D.C. |website=Rand Paul, U.S. Senator for Kentucky |access-date=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124024518/https://www.paul.senate.gov/news/sens-paul-booker-gillibrand-announce-carers-act |dead-url=no }}</ref>。保罗还支持各州以权利为中心的大麻立法，2014年引入了《{{le|罗拉巴克尔–法尔修正案|Rohrabacher–Farr amendment}}》<ref>{{cite web |last1=Ferner |first1=Matt |last2=Reilly |first2=Ryan J. |title=Senate Could Follow House In Blocking DEA From Targeting Medical Marijuana |url=https://www.huffpost.com/entry/rand-paul-medical-marijuana_n_5511734 |accessdate=2020-12-30 |work=HuffPost |date=2014-06-19 |archive-date=2020-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920215527/https://www.huffpost.com/entry/rand-paul-medical-marijuana_n_5511734 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在2018年共同赞助《{{le|通过《州法》加强第十修正案|Strengthening the Tenth Amendment Through Entrusting States (STATES) Act|通过〈州法〉加强第十修正案}}》<ref>{{cite web |title=FAQ: What the STATES Act Would Do, and Why It's a Game-Changer |url=https://www.leafly.com/news/politics/faq-what-the-states-act-would-do-and-why-its-a-game-changer |accessdate=2020-12-30 |work=Leafly |date=2018-06-07 |archive-date=2020-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204185439/https://www.leafly.com/news/politics/faq-what-the-states-act-would-do-and-why-its-a-game-changer |dead-url=no }}</ref> ，并引入其他修正案<ref>{{cite news |last1=Nelson |first1=Steven |title=Rand Paul, Senate Torch-Bearer on Pot Reform, Wants Colleagues on Record |url=https://www.usnews.com/news/articles/2014/07/25/rand-paul-senate-torch-bearer-on-pot-reform-wants-colleagues-on-record |accessdate=2020-12-30 |work=U.S. News & World Report |date=2014-07-25 |archive-date=2020-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806143522/https://www.usnews.com/news/articles/2014/07/25/rand-paul-senate-torch-bearer-on-pot-reform-wants-colleagues-on-record |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Angell |first1=Tom |title=Rand Paul Pushes Marijuana Amendments On Funding Bill |url=https://www.marijuanamoment.net/rand-paul-pushes-marijuana-amendments-funding-bill/ |accessdate=2020-12-30 |work=Marijuana Moment |date=2018-01-20 |archive-date=2020-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102071629/https://www.marijuanamoment.net/rand-paul-pushes-marijuana-amendments-funding-bill/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。保罗在2015年引入了《大麻企业进入银行法》，使得大麻企业增加了进入银行的机会<ref>{{cite web |last1=Thiruvengadam |first1=Meena |title=Rand Paul backs effort to bring banking to legal marijuana businesses |url=https://finance.yahoo.com/news/rand-paul-joins-effort-to-bring-banking-to-legal-marijuana-businesses-034132886.html |accessdate=2020-12-30 |work=Yahoo! Finance |date=2015-07-10 |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202140409/https://finance.yahoo.com/news/rand-paul-joins-effort-to-bring-banking-to-legal-marijuana-businesses-034132886.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

关于[[工业大麻|工业大麻]]种植，保罗支持肯塔基州的合法化努力<ref>{{cite news |last1=Paul |first1=Rand |title=Ky voices: Rand Paul: Legalize hemp to aid Ky. economy |url=https://www.kentucky.com/opinion/op-ed/article44393310.html |accessdate=2020-12-30 |work=Lexington Herald-Leader |date=2012-12-15 |archive-date=2020-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200904012226/https://www.kentucky.com/opinion/op-ed/article44393310.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Gabriel |first1=Trip |title=Hemp Growing Finds Allies of a New Stripe in Kentucky |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/02/13/us/13hemp.html |accessdate=2020-12-30 |work=The New York Times |date=2013-02-12 |archive-date=2020-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125024415/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/02/13/us/13hemp.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>以及联邦一级的合法化努力，在2013年引入了工业大麻种植法<ref>{{cite press release |date=2013-02-14|accessdate=2020-12-30 |title=Sens. McConnell and Paul Co-sponsor Industrial Hemp Legislation |url=https://www.paul.senate.gov/?p=press_release&id=707 |location=Washington, D.C. |website=Rand Paul, U.S. Senator for Kentucky |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130222204726/https://www.paul.senate.gov/?p=press_release&id=707 |archive-date=2013-02-22 |dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在2020年，他引入了《大麻经济动员计划法》（HEMP），将大麻的[[四氢大麻酚|THC]]限制从0.3%提高到1%<ref>{{cite news |last1=Jaeger |first1=Kyle |title=Rand Paul Files Bill To Increase Hemp THC Limit And Address Other Industry Concerns |url=https://www.marijuanamoment.net/rand-paul-files-bill-to-increase-hemp-thc-limit-and-address-other-industry-concerns/ |access-date=2020-12-30 |work=Marijuana Moment |date=2020-12-16 |archive-date=2021-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210218045840/https://www.marijuanamoment.net/rand-paul-files-bill-to-increase-hemp-thc-limit-and-address-other-industry-concerns/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |date=2020-12-15 |access-date=2020-12-30 |title=Dr. Rand Paul Introduces HEMP Act to Relieve Unnecessary Constraints on Hemp Industry, Provide Transparency and Certainty |url=https://www.paul.senate.gov/news/dr-rand-paul-introduces-hemp-act-relieve-unnecessary-constraints-hemp-industry-provide |location=Washington, D.C. |publisher=senate.gov |archive-date=2020-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216211121/https://www.paul.senate.gov/news/dr-rand-paul-introduces-hemp-act-relieve-unnecessary-constraints-hemp-industry-provide |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===政府监察===
