force-the-expiration-of-the-patriot-act-118443 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。保罗称[[爱德华·斯诺登|爱德华·斯诺登]]是“告密者”，他呼吁国家情报局局长{{le|詹姆士·克拉柏|James Clapper}}辞职，因为他在斯诺登曝光的电话元数据项目上“撒谎”<ref>{{cite news |last1=Geller |first1=Eric |title=Rand Paul praises Edward Snowden for doing 'a service' to the U.S. |url=https://www.dailydot.com/debug/rand-paul-edward-snowden-nsa-surveillance-digital-democracy/ |accessdate=2020-12-30 |work=The Daily Dot |date=2015-11-12 |archive-date=2020-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201223091407/https://www.dailydot.com/debug/rand-paul-edward-snowden-nsa-surveillance-digital-democracy/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Trujillo |first1=Mario |title=Paul: Clapper should resign for 'lying to Congress' |url=https://thehill.com/blogs/blog-briefing-room/news/193597-paul-calls-on-clapper-to-resign |accessdate=2020-12-30 |work=The Hill |date=2013-12-19 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112031151/http://thehill.com/blogs/blog-briefing-room/news/193597-paul-calls-on-clapper-to-resign |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他还对奥巴马政府提出了集体诉讼，要求终止该项目<ref>{{cite news |last1=Bolton |first1=Alexander |title=Paul sues Obama over NSA spying |url=https://thehill.com/homenews/senate/198206-paul-sues-obama-to-halt-nsa-surveillance-of-phone-data |accessdate=2020-12-30 |work=The Hill |date=2014-02-12 |archive-date=2020-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806165423/https://thehill.com/homenews/senate/198206-paul-sues-obama-to-halt-nsa-surveillance-of-phone-data |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年，保罗在[[加州大学伯克利分校|加州大学伯克利分校]]发表了题为“N.S.A.与您的隐私”的演讲<ref>{{cite news |last1=Peters |first1=Jeremy W. |title=Rand Paul, Warning About Spying, Faults Obama |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/03/20/us/politics/rand-paul-speaks-at-berkeley.html |accessdate=2020-12-30 |work=The New York Times |date=2014-03-19 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111162549/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/03/20/us/politics/rand-paul-speaks-at-b