===气候变化===
保罗没有完全接受[[关于气候变化的科学观点|关于气候变化的科学共识]]，即[[全球变暖|全球变暖]]是真实的、不断发展的，主要是由人类造成的。保罗曾表示，污染排放要受到“繁重的监管”<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/plum-line/wp/2014/05/12/where-the-2016-gop-contenders-stand-on-climate-change/ |title=Where the 2016 GOP contenders stand on climate change |last=Waldman |first=Paul |date=2014-05-12 |newspaper=The Washington Post|access-date=2021-01-11|dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820082811/https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/plum-line/wp/2014/05/12/where-the-2016-gop-contenders-stand-on-climate-change/ |archive-date=2020-08-20}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://thehill.com/policy/energy-environment/204235-paul-science-behind-climate-change-not-conclusive |title=Rand Paul: Science behind climate change 'not conclusive' |last=Barron-Lopez |first=Laura |date=2014-04-23 |newspaper=The Hill |access-date=2021-01-11 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821101302/http://thehill.com/policy/energy-environment/204235-paul-science-behind-climate-change-not-conclusive |archive-date=2020-08-21}}</ref>。2018年，保罗呼吁对[[国家科学基金会|国家科学基金会]]的一项拨款进行调查，这项拨款用于对气象学家进行气候变化科学方面的教育。保罗说，这笔拨款“不是科学”，而是“宣传”<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/congress/gop-senators-challenge-funding-global-warming-education-program-n885221 |title=GOP senators challenge funding for global warming education program |last=Rainey |first=James |work=NBC News |date=2018-06-21 |access-date=2021-01-11 |language=en-US |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200314004451/https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/congress/gop-senators-challenge-funding-global-warming-education-program-n885221 |archive-date=2020-03-14}}</ref>。

